    "problemStatement": "<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><span>Puzzles are a fun and exciting way to sharpen your brain! They\u2019re often used in exams and job interviews to test logical and analytical skills. Whether you\u2019re a school or college student preparing for tests or just want to challenge yourself, solving puzzles can improve your problem-solving abilities.</span></p><figure class=\"image\"><img alt=\"how_to_solve_this_puzzle_\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20251217102543010715/how_to_solve_this_puzzle_.webp\" srcset=\"https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20251217102543010715/how_to_solve_this_puzzle_.webp 800w,https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20251217102543010715/how_to_solve_this_puzzle_-100.webp 100w,https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20251217102543010715/how_to_solve_this_puzzle_-200.webp 200w,https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20251217102543010715/how_to_solve_this_puzzle_-300.webp 300w,https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20251217102543010715/how_to_solve_this_puzzle_-660.webp 660w,https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20251217102543010715/how_to_solve_this_puzzle_-768.webp 768w\" width=\"800\"/><figcaption> </figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"most-asked-puzzles-in-interview2025\" style=\"text-align:left\"><span>Most Asked Puzzles in Interview(2025)</span></h2><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><span>If puzzles are stopping you from doing well in interviews, you\u2019re in the right place to get help. These 10 puzzle interview questions are enough to build a strong foundation for you.</span></p><ol><li value=\"1\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/gfg-academy/puzzle-the-burning-candles/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>The Burning Ropes</span></a></li><li value=\"2\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/puzzle-9-find-the-fastest-3-horses/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>The 25 Horses</span></a></li><li value=\"3\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/puzzle-18-torch-and-bridge/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>The Bridge Crossing Problem</span></a></li><li value=\"4\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/puzzle-19-poison-and-rat/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>The Poisoned Bottle</span></a></li><li value=\"5\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/puzzle-set-35-2-eggs-and-100-floors/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>The Two-Egg Problem</span></a></li><li value=\"6\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/puzzle-water-jug-problem/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Four Gallon Problem</span></a></li><li value=\"7\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/puzzle-number-of-legs-in-palace/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Number of Legs in the Palace</span></a></li><li value=\"8\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/puzzle-six-houses-p-q-r-s-t-and-u/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>The Six Houses</span></a></li><li value=\"9\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/puzzle-8-balls-problem/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>The 8 Ball Problem</span></a></li><li value=\"10\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/puzzle-13-100-prisoners-with-redblack-hats/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Prisoners with Red/Black Hats</span></a></li></ol><h2 id=\"1-analytical-mathematical-puzzles\" style=\"text-align:left\"><b><strong>1. Analytical / Mathematical Puzzles</strong></b></h2><table><thead><tr><th style=\"width: 233.333px;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>Puzzle Title</span></p></th><th style=\"width: 233.333px;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-